title: O'NEILL PSYCHO RG8 2011/12
description: The Psycho Re•Generate Series takes the best aspects of our incredible Z.E.N. Zip closure found in our Psycho wetsuits and uses this same technology in a front-zip entry. The 2012 F.U.Z.E. closure system has an easier entry and exit, along with added warmth using RG8- Air Firewall. Tested by Team O'Neill in the most frigid waters across the globe.
